ow=\"scroll\"><mn>0</mn></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"0.25 newton meters\"><math alttext=\"0.25 newton meters\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>0.25</mn><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace></mstyle><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mtext>N</mtext></mstyle><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mo>⋅</mo></mstyle><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mtext>m</mtext></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1.0 newton meter\"><math alttext=\"1.0 newton meter\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1.0</mn><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace></mstyle><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mtext>N</mtext></mstyle><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mo>⋅</mo></mstyle><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mtext>m</mtext></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2.0 newton meters\"><math alttext=\"2.0 newton meters\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2.0</mn><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace></mstyle><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mtext>N</mtext></mstyle><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mo>⋅</mo></mstyle><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mtext>m</mtext></mstyle></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":2}]